snippet.title: Angels & Demons: Demo 4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Angels & Demons: https://www.journoid.net

Platformer, RPG, Rhythm Game?!
Angels & Demons is a multi-genre mash-up!
Embark on a quest with your guardian angel to save the world from demons!

- Fluid platformer mechanics!
- Mario & Luigi inspired turn-based battles!
- osu!mania-like rhythm game + other rhythm elements!
- 5+ hours of game-play!

Link Tree: https://linktr.ee/journoid
OST Download: https://journoid.bandcamp.com/album/angels-demons-demo-4-ost

Thanks for watching!
